parser = MockedSiteParser()
builder = MangaBuilder(parser)
manga = builder.get_manga_volumes(vol_nums=[1], preferred_name=
    'smelly_pancakes')
v1 = Volume(number=1, file_path=
    '/tmp/smelly_pancakes/smelly_pancakes_volume_1.pdf', upload_path=Path(
    '/smelly_pancakes/smelly_pancakes_volume_1.pdf'))
img1 = open('tests/test_files/jpgs/test-manga_1_1.jpg', 'rb')
img2 = open('tests/test_files/jpgs/test-manga_1_2.jpg', 'rb')
pages = [(1, img1.read()), (2, img2.read())]
v1.pages = pages
assert manga.volume[1] == v1
